            <title><![CDATA[The Outlast Trials Update Includes A Ton Of Free (And Unsettling) Cosmetics]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-outlast-trials-new-season-includes-a-ton-of-free-and-unsettling-cosmetics/1100-6530360/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
